  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span style=\"font-size:0px;font-family:ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;, &quot;Noto Color Emoji&quot;;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n  <div style=\"font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;font-size:15px;box-sizing:border-box;text-decoration-thickness:initial;border-radius:12px;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;text-align:left;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;padding:8px;letter-spacing:normal;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1.75;font-style:normal;text-transform:none;background:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.067) 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.067) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 32px), repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.067) 0px, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.067) 1px, transparent 1px, transparent 32px) rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;\">\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 许给了微软一笔分手费，</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2500 亿美金</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">然后说：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们都可以去找别人了</span></strong></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100023995\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2917888563049853\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1364\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;border-style:solid;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;text-align:left;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;margin:0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYoK9h8gk64nJVLmwNTZwaPWuMzoxiaic7bYbK1AYuHH3lEmmd2XqmjElUicszN9uP8uofibeFHoAJZu9Q/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"705\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=95f31506&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYoK9h8gk64nJVLmwNTZwaPWuMzoxiaic7bYbK1AYuHH3lEmmd2XqmjElUicszN9uP8uofibeFHoAJZu9Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://openai.com/index/next-chapter-of-microsoft-openai-partnership/\" target=\"_blank\">https://openai.com/index/next-chapter-of-microsoft-openai-partnership/</a></span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 在官网上发布了这项声明，核心变化包括：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"padding:0px 0px 0px 0.2em;margin:0px 12px 16px 16px;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.8;list-style:disc;text-align:left;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• OpenAI 承诺采购&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">2500 亿美元</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;Azure 服务，但微软失去优先供应权</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">•&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">微软可以独立或与第三方合作追求 AGI</span></strong></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• OpenAI 可以和第三方联合开发产品，能发布开源模型</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• 微软持股从 32.5% 稀释到 27%，投资价值 1350 亿美元</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"margin:0.5em 8px;text-indent:-1em;display:block;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">• AGI 认定要独立专家小组验证</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <blockquote style=\"padding:1em 1em 1em 16px;margin:0px 8px 32px;font-size:15px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(229, 229, 229) rgb(198, 110, 73);line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:6px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05) 0px 4px 6px;border-width:0px 0px 0px 4px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <p style=\"margin:0px;display:block;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:1em;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.8;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">一对老夫妻，开始玩开放式关系</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 19.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(198, 110, 73);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">钱的交易</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 承诺采购 2500 亿美元 Azure 服务</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">题外话：微软 2024 财年全年营收 2450 亿美元，OpenAI 则为 37 亿美金</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(198, 110, 73);font-weight: bold;\">OpenAI 未来要给微软的钱，比微软当下的年收入还多</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但微软失去了什么?</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">优先购买权</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">原文：Right of First Refusal</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">以前：OpenAI 买算力，必须先问微软</span><span leaf=\"\">现在：OpenAI 想买谁家的都行</span><span leaf=\"\">这是个微妙的平衡</span></p>\n   <figure style=\"margin:1.5em 8px;font-size:15px;border-width:0px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;border-style:solid;text-align:left;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100023972\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.2303120356612185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1346\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;border-width:0px;border-style:solid;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);display:block;vertical-align:middle;max-width:100%;text-align:left;line-height:1.75;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size:15px;margin:0.1em auto 0.5em;border-radius:8px;box-shadow:rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 8px;width:100%;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/2icSMc1VBIYoK9h8gk64nJVLmwNTZwaPWeuv2hg4IShzbaIe8daItyOMOib5johgYALMTicWbiaSdNvO7Y7GAE23LA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"546\" data-cropsely2=\"269\" data-backw=\"546\" data-backh=\"672\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=53e8192a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F2icSMc1VBIYoK9h8gk64nJVLmwNTZwaPWeuv2hg4IShzbaIe8daItyOMOib5johgYALMTicWbiaSdNvO7Y7GAE23LA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n    <figcaption style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 0.8em;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">\n     <span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 现在的股权信息</span>\n    </figcaption>\n   </figure>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">微软持股从 32.5% 降到 27%，账面价值 1350 亿美元</span></p>\n   <h2 style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-size: 19.5px;font-weight: bold;margin: 4em auto 2em;text-align: center;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;display: table;padding: 0.3em 1em;background: rgb(198, 110, 73);border-radius: 8px;box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1) 0px 4px 6px;color: white !important;\"><span leaf=\"\">自由的背后</span></h2>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">微软可以独立去做 AGI 了</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">当然，也可找第三方，比如 DeepSeek 去搞</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但如果微软想用 OpenAI 的技术来做 AGI，有个限制</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans 