der-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">在公告里，这叫做</span><span leaf=\"\">The next chapter of the Microsoft–OpenAI partnership</span><span leaf=\"\">与微软合作的新篇章，或者关系升级</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但换句话说：</span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;border-width: 0px;border-style: solid;border-color: rgb(229, 229, 229);font-weight: bold;text-align: left;line-height: 1.75;font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: inherit;color: rgb(198, 110, 73);margin: 24px 0px 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">体面的松绑，可以找别人了</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">OpenAI 用 2500 亿美元买了自由</span><span leaf=\"\">微软拿钱放手，但保住了技术使用权</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:24px 8px 8px;letter-spacing:0.1em;font-size:16px;border-color:rgb(229, 229, 229);line-height:2;box-sizing:border-box;word-break:break-all;border-width:0px;font-family:-apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;border-style:solid;opacity:0.9;text-align:justify;\"><span leaf=\"\">但 AGI 一旦实现，这些条款都会重新洗牌</span><span leaf=\"\">到那时会怎样，谁也说不准</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度解读 OpenAI 与微软合作模式的重大调整，OpenAI 以 2500 亿美元 Azure 采购承诺换取更大独立性，微软则获得独立追求 AGI 的自由。",
